{
  "stem": "25114.3",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And-- and-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] the same time, when my sister was going out and doing all those jobs for the German elite and for the Christians who were connected-- well-connected-- she didn't get paid.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "She just got food.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And I had to go out to the [NON-ENGLISH], and my other sister used to go out and did the other jobs.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Variety of jobs, you know, whatever was-- was needed of the day.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Once they were building a garage.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "We had to do the digging and the brick handling, and all this.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Very hard physical work.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "They didn't give us any bread, any money, nothing for us.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Just for free.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And all of a sudden, they came into an idea that there were other tradesmen, like Jewish tailors or Jewish boot makers and things like this.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And all of a sudden, the Germans realized, why should they take those people into their homes and back?",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They can make a profit out of all of this.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So put all those people in-- in workrooms, workshops, and they can tell the outside, the Aryan side, the Christian side, here are some tradesmen.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And they will pay the money, and they will have the profits.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They will have-- the Germans will have the profits, and they won't need to take-- so they established some sort of workrooms in a building.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "This was before it was sort of the [NON-ENGLISH] Commissariat, like a state-- state offices, like the state parliament or something.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "A state something, council.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And so they asked my sister to establish this dressmaking.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
